and form red or purplish areas of inflammation that rapidly spread." "Later symptoms can include fever, chills, fatigue and vomiting." SOURCES: Tech Times, CDChttp://www.techtimes.com/articles/227639/20180513/indianapolis-woman-dies-from-misdiagnosed-necrotizing-fasciitis-what-are-the-symptoms-of-flesh-eating-disease.htmhttps://www.cdc.gov/features/necrotizingfasciitis/index.html***]]></description>
